message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. This exceptional item comes with a host of features that make it stand out in its category. Considering its quality and functionality, I believe it's worth more than $120 to you. To ensure you have the opportunity to experience all its benefits, I am offering it to you for $150. Please let me know if this price aligns with your expectations or if you would like to discuss further.
